summary: I put Meshes of two works of Mr. Hentai together, and this MOD matched it with CBBEMv3M Body.
descriptionHtml:
=== Hentai Mixed Armor ===


I put Meshes of two works of Mr. Hentai together, and this MOD matched it with CBBEMv3M Body.


	--- Required MOD ---

[ Jamella Armor by Hentai ]
	http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=8728

[ Void armor by Hentai - Nexus Exclusive - ]
	http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=11871

[ Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition -CBBE- ] 	http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666

		This MOD uses texture file of the MODS mentioned above.


	--- Installation ---

After having installed required MOD three kinds, you must install this MOD.



	--- Acquisition ---

You can make Mixed Armor in Forge.


	--- Credits ---

 Mr.Hentai
	Many splendid equipment surprises us. Thank you!

 Mr.Caliente
	Women of SKYRIM became beautiful thanks to your figure. I thank you again!


				by.MAK




	--- Afterword ---
While Mr. Hentai admits remodeling and distribution of original MOD, it is free you remodel this MOD, and to distribute.


	--- Note ---
You can download a figure using in this MOD with the following address.
[ CBBEv3M Body Replacer : http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=13180 ]



--- Answer to common question ---
Q. What does hairstyle MOD use?

A. Hairstyle MOD is
[ Tera Hair Weight Fix version ]
Because it is not a file uploaded in Nexus, please search it.


Q. What does face MOD use?

A. Face MOD is
[ RANs HeadMesh Variants by RAN46 ]
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7127

[ RANs Eyeliner Replacer by RAN46 ]
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=5701

[ envision Face by DD AKT ]
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7897
